{"tid":2319918,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"運輸工涉藏雷射筆被控 自辯透露警署內遭蒙面警硬物扑頭暈倒","createTime":"2020-12-10T11:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T12:22:14.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8c1025a74fe1b35ad880595300ba2020eb936e2e","tid":2319918,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"去年9月22日有市民在港鐵太子站外聚集，其間有人在毗連的旺角警署外噴漆。防暴警衝出驅散時，拘捕中年運輸工人，控以在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器及拒捕兩罪。裁判官裁定案件表證成立，被告出庭自辯，透露當晚無故被制服，復遭警員用警棍亂毆，到被押解入旺角警署後，更遭一名蒙面警員以硬物扑頭，令他頭破血流兼暈倒，腰纏鐵鏈送院醫治。<br />\n<br />\n被告續指，被鎖上手銬後，有兩名警員一左一右挾持他，後頸再被另一警員叉著，押解往警署，<span class=\"red\">途經停車場斜路時突遭一名蒙面警員以硬物扑頭</span>。被告即時暈倒，幾秒後被人拍醒，並帶他往報案室處理傷勢。其間有警員在他面前檢視背囊內的證物，隨後以鐵鏈鎖腰方式將他送往廣華醫院，當時才有警員向他宣佈拘捕。"},{"pid":"71cc15ab6d62c48604982be4f75ff3d02c08695d","tid":2319918,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:49:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/4ZRMXKCGYNAGFEWKLHDAKS5MCU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2F4ZRMXKCGYNAGFEWKLHDAKS5MCU%2F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYptUqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=95defed5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2F4ZRMXKCGYNAGFEWKLHDAKS5MCU%2F&h=a8f6c1db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/4ZRMXKCGYNAGFEWKLHDAKS5MCU/</a>"},{"pid":"e3dd5194d825e42c05b785074e55e32bcebea9cf","tid":2319918,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ec365f60b540dc623cfa8b05f579834c17f645","tid":2319918,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T11:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img